flowchart TD

%% --- KI MODULE FLOW ---

subgraph KI_Module[KI Module Flow]

A1[ORMD Maker<br/>Creates KI] --> A2[ORMD Checker<br/>Approves / Rejects]

A2 -->|Approved| A3[Department Maker & Checker<br/>View KI]

A3 --> A4[Department Maker<br/>Adds KI Data
• Backend Upload
• CSV Upload
• Web Entry]

A4 --> A5[Department Checker<br/>Final Approval]

A5 --> A6[Final KI Sent for Reporting]

A2 -->|Rejected| A1

end


%% --- IMM MODULE FLOW ---

subgraph IMM_Module[IMM Module Flow]

B1[Incident Owner<br/>Creates & Reports Incident]
--> B2[Reviewer<br/>Reviews]

B2 --> B3[Approver<br/>From Different Branch]

B3 -->|Approved| B4[Sent for Recommendation/Closure]
B3 -->|Rejected| B2

end